│ I->getMetadata(LLVMContext::MD_noduplicate))\n  return       │
│ false;\n```\n\nThis change will make the function bail out   │
│ early if it encounters an `or` instruction with the          │
│ `noduplicate` metadata, which corresponds to the `disjoint`  │
