│ static bool checkOrAndOpImpliedByOther(const Instruction *I, │
│ unsigned OpNo,\n                                             │
│ ConstraintSystem &CS,\n                                      │
│ const DataLayout &DL) {\n      assert((I->getOpcode() ==     │
│ Instruction::Or || I->getOpcode() == Instruction::And) &&\n  │
│ ```\n*   **Proposed Change**:\n    ```cpp\n    static bool   │
│ checkOrAndOpImpliedByOther(const Instruction *I, unsigned    │
│ OpNo,\n                                                      │
