│ check to skip this optimization for `or` instructions with   │
│ the `noduplicate` (`disjoint`) flag, we prevent the pass     │
│ from introducing `poison` and ensure the correctness of the  │
│ transformation. This targeted fix resolves the bug while     │
│ leaving the optimization intact for regular `or`             │
│ instructions where it is beneficial."})                      │
